I heard Gu Yansheng was wanted
for intentional injury

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:57.680
and kidnapping.

00:01:57.799 --> 00:01:58.519
Yes.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:00.359
He kidnapped Yunyun.

