00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:32.360
Me?

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:34.879
How could I do that?

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:36.439
I'm just a girl.

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:37.960
So what if you're a girl?

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:39.599
The old madam was a woman too.

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:42.400
And she still made the Gu Group thrive.

00:02:42.919 --> 00:02:45.280
Now you're the only heir
left in the Gu family.

00:02:45.719 --> 00:02:47.759
Be its acting head for now.

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.000
Later,

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.280
