00:05:27.399 --> 00:05:28.360
Don't you get it?

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:31.660
(Ranked No. 1 in the Grade)

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.600
Why?

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:37.319
I'm not worse than anyone else.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:39.519
